    <item>
      <title>期权显示比特币交易者正在为更严重的暴跌做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/options-show-bitcoin-traders-are-preparing-for-a-deeper-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权表明，随着对持有加密货币的美国交易所交易基金的需求开始减弱，交易员正在准备迎接比特币的长期下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/options-show-bitcoin-traders-are-preparing-for-a-deeper-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 17:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
